title: Blue Moon
description: Perhaps one of the most well known names of Cook Islands Music, Brother Love (Rahui Vaka) stormed onto the scene in 1996 with his hit song Ruketekete Te Mamae (aka Roimata).  After many years as a percussion musician he decided to exercise his own vocal skill, and since then has released several albums as a solo artist.  This, his second volume features many of his original compositions and favourite tunes.
